<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3125] When a SolrCore registers in zk there may be stale leader state in the clusterstate.json.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3125</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This can be a problem when stop the whole cluster and then start it - a leader that has not yet showed up in the cluster state may see a stale leader and try to recover from it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12542270">SOLR-3125</key>
            <summary>When a SolrCore registers in zk there may be stale leader state in the clusterstate.json.</summary>
