                            <comment id="13206324" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Sun, 12 Feb 2012 01:16:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;a workaround - on registering, instead of getting the leader from the cluster state, we go right to the ephemeral zk node&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13206618" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Mon, 13 Feb 2012 01:40:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve committed this work around, but need to consider if there is anything more we should try to do.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13210745" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Sat, 18 Feb 2012 01:55:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is good for now - works - any improvement can go to another issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
